<h2>Important Safety Precautions</h2>
<h3>READ BEFORE PLACEMENT: RISK OF HARM!</h3>

<div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="column">
    <img src="indoor.png" alt="couch and lamp icon" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;">
